data.description: Discover the epitome of comfortable living, where comfort meets convenience. Almost every room features ceiling fans, ensuring a pleasant atmosphere year-round. With 2 kitchens, meal prep is a breeze, while the gas fireplace downstairs and in the living room offer cozy warmth and charm. Relax and unwind in the light & bright sunroom upstairs. Abundant storage includes an attic and an expansive food storage room downstairs. Washer and dryer on main level and basement. Step outside to the fenced backyard, a retreat with garden space and thriving fruit trees—perfect for outdoor enthusiasts and avid gardeners. This meticulously designed residence combines practicality with serene living. - Schedule a showing now!
